Subject: Re: [T2] 71 Front Brake Hoses

The correct hose yer looking for is VW 281-611-775 B.  Fits Front 71-79 Type
2 as well as Front 71-79 Super Beetle & Convertible.  Fits Left or Right.

http://www.airheadparts.com/viewDetail.asp?strMasterCat=&idproduct=5078
